result.title: My Hero Academia Season 7
result.author: Bones
result.description:
The seventh season of Boku no Hero Academia. Note: The season was preceded by a 4-episode special titled 'Boku no Hero Academia: Memories' recapping events from the 6th season along with adding a few minutes of new material each episode.

Other name(s): Boku no Hero Academia 7
